==English==

===Noun===

'''circumstance'''

#That which [[attend]]s, or [[relate]]s to, or in some way [[affect]]s, a [[fact]] or [[event]]; an attendant thing or [[state]] of things.
#An event; a fact; a particular [[incident]].
#Circumlocution; [[detail]].
#Condition in regard to worldly estate; state of [[property]]; situation; surroundings.

====Translations====
*Finnish: [[olosuhteet]] ''pl'' (1), [[olot]] ''pl'' (1)

===Verb===

'''to circumstance'''

#To place in a particular situation; to supply relative incidents.

